Overview
- Answer the customer needs and facilitate the decision-making process
- Three level of intelligence:
  - Strategic #Chiến lược
    Client characteristics: C-executives (less technical/big picture in mind)
  - Operational #Vận hành
    Client characteristics: SOC leader/ CERT leader (technical/broader picture in mind)
  - Tactical 
    Client characteristics: fellow analysists (technical)
Challenge
- Adapt your reports to the audience
- Adapt your speech to the audience
- Find suitable format when sharing IoCs

